data.description: Acreage! This charming home is set in a quiet subdivision that gives you a country feel. Sitting on slightly less than an acre, there is plenty of room with the outbuildings for storage of toys, trailers, and separate access to property with an easement in the back. Come see this 5 bedroom 3 bath home that features a wood fireplace and on demand water heater for unlimited hot water! Property has an option for $400/year to use an additional half acre for storage beyond property line. If you're looking for a property with a good sized home, upgrades in the house, and a country feeling with close access to city needs, this is the one! Come see what this home has to offer...
